<br>
&quot;La Lame Du Fantôme&quot;<br>
(The Blade of the Ghost)<br>
<br>
Story &amp; Art by Chaos Theory<br>
<br>
Intro<br>
World War 3 ended on June 18th, 2036. The 33 year war had ended, and not one nation had come ontop. Luckily for the human race, it was not fought with nuclear weapons. Most of the smaller countries, though, were obliterated, lost to the sands of time. Over the decades that passed, mankind built itself back up to what it was before. Technological advances were in sight. Everything seemed fine.<br>
<br>
And it was. For hundreds of years. Technology had become extremely sophisticated. By 2245 synthetic humans made up 15% Earth's population. Most of Earth's defense forces were &quot;Synthetics&quot;. Synthetics could be easily controlled. They had no free will.<br>
<br>
Time passed. Faster than light speed travel was no longer a fantasy, And Earth was abandon.<br>
<br>
More time passed. An alien race known as the &quot;Fantsym&quot; now poses a major threat to mankind's survival.<br>
<br>
It is now 4579, and the unimaginable will soon happen...<br>
<br>
